{
  "texts": [
    "In the fifth section, the experimental part, we evaluate the DIC-Transformer on our self-constructed dataset (ADCG-18).",
    "The dataset contains 3,971 images, 9,040 instances of disease areas, and 3,971 textual descriptions.",
    "Experiments demonstrate that the DIC-Transformer method applied to the ADCG-18 dataset can address the proposed research topic.",
    "The article's contributions are divided into the following three parts:",
    "• A method for plant disease image classification is proposed."
  ]
}